No fewer than eighteen  candidates have been returned opposed  in the on going APC national convention. Some of the candidates includes; Comrade Adams Oshiomhole national chairman, Alhaji Ibrahim Masari national secretary,  Zakari Mohammed North central leader,  Abubakar Sadiq, zonal secretary North East among others. Voting for other positions is presently on going. Also, two factions from Delta led by Ortega Emerhor and Great Ogboru clashed. This has led to commotion at the Delta state stand.  